{
  "stem": "17625.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were plenty-- plenty times which we saw with our eyes, [INAUDIBLE]-- and the other SS fuhrers, you know, they brought in their-- their-- their-- their friends, girlfriends, ladies, whatever this is.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "SS, also.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- if they want to make a show [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they-- they-- they killed before they went in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The SS just turned around and gave them a bullet in the back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was fun.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- and this was to show off what he can do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was the guy, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And another guy was there, a scharfuhrer also, who were-- who were responsible for the massacre from the-- from the few hundred people which were before my commander, which-- which which I heard before New Year's they-- they cleaned up the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because they said they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or they-- they think they-- they organize something, and they clean them up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'42.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before I got there, and before they-- I-- and then they-- they brought in the others under commander, which they came from-- from Bialystok, from Lomza, from Grodno.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from-- from [INAUDIBLE] there, from near Warsaw there, and then another town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mainly Polish?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Little Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, Polish, we were from-- if you-- from Bialystok, and from Lomza, This was Polish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were French.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were Holland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were Slavs, Slavics.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one-- one Frenchman, Maurice, he came from Algiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From Algiers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He must have been in Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent him-- when the Warsaw ghetto was-- the uprising, they sent him to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "W Because he didn't speak Polish, and not Jewish, but French.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And most probably they brought him there to hang, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what I heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, in the camp?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
